<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="MTA44">
<l>tamarukanta tevvuruva mavvuruvan tāṉē</l>
<l>tamarukanta teppērmaṟ ṟappēr – tamarukan</l>
<l>tevvaṇṇañ cintit timaiyā tirupparē</l>
<l>yavvaṇṇa māḻiyā ṉām</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Whatever form delights his people is just the form,</l>
<l>whatever name delights his people again is the name, whatever colour</l>
<l>his people delightedly keep thinking of without blinking,</l>
<l>that is the colour of him with the discus.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
